metadata.name: III
metadata.description: In a world increasingly dominated by the virtually intangible, “Oh Bondage Up Yours!” seeks to provide a momentary reprieve from the very same digitally-shackled environment it occupies - sensory elements of physically-fetishized leather and metal are captured on analogue video equipment, offering a stark reminder of the material realm still readily available to [yet increasingly neglected by] us, should we choose with intention to inhabit our bodies and revisit + explore with a profound sense of freedom this 3D reality we continue to call “home”.
